<title>USA: Saville Systems names Chris Hanson CFO.</title>
<headline>Saville Systems names Chris Hanson CFO.</headline>
<dateline>BURLINGTON, Mass. 1997-03-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Saville Systems Plc Monday said it named Chris Hanson as chief financial officer, replacing Marc Venator who was promoted to the new position of chief operating officer.</p>
<p>Hanson previously worked at System Software Associates Inc, where he was treasurer of the manufacturing software provider.</p>
<p>Saville is a leading provider of convergent billing and customer care solutions to the telecommunications industry.</p>
